reviewText: I just started watching game of thrones. I'd heard a lot of people praise the series, so I gave it a shot. I'm hooked. Ended up buying all the episodes of season 3 on amazon video before this even came in the mail. I like having discs in my collection, so it was worth the buy. The material used for the cover is pretty decent quality. Packaging inside is nice as well. Very satisfied with my purchase.
Amazing as always. Best show on earth!

Well it was certainly Game of Thrones. Everything thing was in good order. All the people that were supposed to die did; all the ones who were supposed to be horribly maimed or traumatized were, so a good buy overall. I'd like to buy the 6th book, but I can't seem to find it anywhere...

The discs within were so smudged on the back that they would not play without cleaning.  I thought I was buying new... so don't understand why the season 3 and season 4 appeared to be used or poorly handled.

This season is the best season yet (since I haven't seen all of the seasons available on DVD). The costumes and scenery in this season are even more spectacular than in season 2! I found the battle scene to be especially interesting. Very realistic. The attention to detail in this series is superb. Each episode is like a mini movie. Most of the TV shows these days are garbage but this one does not disappoint. Keep the awesome GOT episodes coming! I will cry when the series is all over. 5 stars from this viewer :)
